  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="16763147">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jy1988/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u18603743-4.jpg" alt="诗人依赖着月亮" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16763147/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16763147/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jy1988/" class=" " title="诗人依赖着月亮">诗人依赖着月亮</a>
                (小酌二两，敬这灿烂骄阳)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="16763147">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">真正不羁的灵魂不会真的去计较什么。因为他们的内心深处里有国王般的骄傲。 
</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16763147/">(<span class="">7回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-02-16 11:47</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">69人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                真正不羁的灵魂不会真的去计较什么。因为他们的内心深处里有国王般的骄傲。 

